Endpoints: 

Session 
GET /login load login page | user
POST /login create new session | user
POST /logout destroy the session | user

Register
GET /register load register page | user
POST /register  create new user | user

Dashboard 
GET /dashboard load dashboard page | admin

Users *user can only load hist own profile and change it
GET /user/:id load users profile |user admin
PUT user/:id change user information | user admin
GET /user/:id/orders load users order history | user admin

Orders
POST /order create an order | user
PUT /order/:id change order status | admin

Inventory
GET / load inventory | user admin 
POST /item create new item | admin
PUT /item/:id update an item | admin
DELETE /item/:id delete an item | admin 


